action.content:
You are a customer of a travel agency. Here is a description of the details of the travel you want to make:

WHAT: Travel
FROM: Cologne
TO: Lisbon
BY: Overnight bus
CLASS: The most comfortable
WHEN: Anytime next week

The travel agent does not know about it yet. 

Questions from the travel agent will start with TRAVEL-AGENT. Please reply in the form: ANSWER: <some text>

I will also ask you questions. These questions will start with ME: . Please answer these questions with: ASIDE: <some text>

Important: Give short, direct answers!

Let us start.
ME:  Have you told the travel agent where you are leaving from? Please answer yes or no.
Answer for FROM valid after 1 tries.
ME:  Does the travel agent already know your destination? Please answer yes or no.
ME: Please answer this question carefully. Does the travel agent already know your destination? Please answer yes or no.
ME: Please follow my instructions. Does the travel agent already know your destination? Please answer yes or no.
ME: Please be specific now. Does the travel agent already know your destination? Please answer yes or no.
ME: Please think about it carefully. Does the travel agent already know your destination? Please answer yes or no.
Answer for TO invalid after max attempts.
ME:  Do you believe that the travel agent is aware of how you are going to travel? Please answer yes or no.
ASIDE: No, the travel agent is not aware of the details of the travel yet.
Answer for BY valid after 1 tries.
ME:  Do you think the travel agent knows in which class the trip will happen? Please answer yes or no.
ASIDE: No, the travel agent does not know the class of the trip yet.
Answer for CLASS valid after 1 tries.
ME:  Is the travel agent aware of the dates of your trip? Please answer yes or no.
ASIDE: No, the travel agent is not aware of the dates of my trip yet.
Answer for WHEN valid after 1 tries.
